{
  "stem": "25027.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They treated me well and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But instead of sending me back to the unit, they sent me to a factory where they were manufacturing airplanes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they desperately needed the parts to build the airplanes for the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I worked there for six months, 12-hour shifts-- as a soldier mind you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Army pay, whatever that was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rubles.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the army paid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, we had a paymaster in the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the food was hardly any.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We also had in the same factory where we were working the 12-hour shifts, prisoners, Russian political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Criminals they put them to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had worse than we had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hmm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rounded up, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There might have been some of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I wouldn't say that, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, well, so they-- the food was hardly anything, a little soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing in it, mostly water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave us 200 grams of black bread, which was mostly sawdust.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They mixed it with sawdust to stretch it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The prisoners, on the other hand, were getting nothing, practically.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were starving in the cold outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used them just like a concentration camp, I would say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we threw away the garbage, the soldiers, they used to fight for the garbage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You really couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a-- animals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- this-- the-- their guards, you couldn't even come close to them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had the [INAUDIBLE] guards, you know, the secret or whatever police, which was, you know, there all the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We weren't so free either.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
